videos.headline: Demon Deacons go deep on first play
videos.description: From their own nine-yard line, QB John Wolford airs it out to Scotty Washington for a 47-yard gain.

videos.headline: Wolford reads, keeps, and scores
videos.description: Wake Forest QB John Wolford keeps the read-option and scores from one yard out as Wake Forest takes an early 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Demon Deacons' defense containing Jackson early
videos.description: The Wake Forest front forces Lamar Jackson out of the pocket and Willie Yarbary deflects Jackson's pass to force a Louisville field goal.

videos.headline: Quick screen turns into quick score for Wake Forest
videos.description: QB John Wolford throws the screen to Greg Dortch who follows his blockers 32 yards for the touchdown as Wake Forest jumps to a 14-3 first quarter lead.

videos.headline: Jackson throws pick after huge block
videos.description: A punishing block buys Lamar Jackson time outside of the pocket, but he is intercepted by Essang Bassey in the end zone.

videos.headline: Dortch beats Louisville defense to pylon on swing pass
videos.description: Wake Forest QB John Wolford brings Greg Dortch over in motion and then throws him a quick swing pass and Dortch dives for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Jackson sparks Louisville with TD run
videos.description: QB Lamar Jackson keep the read-option and sprints to the pylon to score Louisville's first touchdown of the game as the Cardinals trail the Demon Deacons 21-10.

videos.headline: Dortch burns Louisville defense for third TD in ifrst half
videos.description: Wake Forest QB John Wolford brings the defense in with a play-action fake and throws over the middle to Greg Dortch for the 25-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Wake Forest defense swarms and sacks Jackson
videos.description: Lamar Jackson dances in the pocket but cannot escape the relentless Wake Forest defensive front and is sacked by Justin Strnad to force a punt before half.

videos.headline: Dortch's sensational fourth TD is erased by goal line fumble
videos.description: It looks like Greg Dortch has the touchdown of the day by staying on his feet after being wrapped up, but he fumbles just before crossing the goal line giving Louisville the ball and erasing the called touchdown.

videos.headline: Jackson freezes on the goal line and hops into end zone
videos.description: Lamar Jackson keeps Louisville in it by completely freezing as a defender dives out of bounds and then hops into the end zone for the score.

videos.headline: Jackson not quitting with late TD run
videos.description: Down 18 points with under two  minutes left, Lamar Jackson rips a 55-yard touchdown run as Louisville trails 35-25 late in the fourth.

videos.headline: Wolford secures Wake Forest win with TD pass
videos.description: QB John Wolford throws the final of his five touchdowns on the day to Chuck Wade for the 44-yard score as Wolford tallies 461 passing yards on the day.
